&#160; &#160; &#160; 7.) The authoress claims revelation, and the Church decided it was not revelation.</font></strong></p><p align="center"><strong><font color="#0000ff" size="3">What Catholics Read</font></strong></p><p><strong><font size="3">&#160; &#160; &#160; There are hundreds of examples justifying the condemnation of this <em>Poem</em>, but three examples are sufficient to illustrate how Jesus and Mary talk, offered with the caveat that this is blasphemous material.<br />
